|**Prevent duplicates**|Shopify retries + network instability can cause duplicates, requiring idempotency.|No native deduplication.|Configurable deduplication detects and drops duplicates.
For Shopify, using the `X-Shopify-Event-Id` header as the identifier is recommended.|
