**Hookdeck's Deduplication:** Hookdeck can be configured to deduplication events before they reach your application.
Configure the `X-Shopify-Event-Id` header as the deduplication key to ensure each unique webhook is processed once.
This works regardless of how many times Shopify attempts delivery.
Pair this with application-level idempotency for defense in depth.
...
Even with Deduplication enabled, implement idempotency in your application:
```
const processedEvents = new Set();
app.post('/webhooks/shopify', verifyHookdeckSignature, (req, res) => {
const eventId = req.headers['x-hookdeck-eventid'];
// Check if already processed
if (processedEvents.has(eventId)) {
console.log(`Event ${eventId} already processed, skipping`);
return res.status(200).json({ success: true });
}
